    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "A *boreal staff* is chiseled from a cylinder of ice to form a spiky, jagged icicle, its surface gleaming with the colors of the northern lights. It gives the air around you a distinct chill. When used as a weapon, a *boreal staff* is a *+1 striking staff*.",
